<html><head>
</head><title>CHILDREARING PRACTICES</title><body><p>
<center><b>CHILDREARING PRACTICES</b><p>
<b></b><p>
Robert G. Myers and Judith L. Evans<p>
<p>
The Secretariat of<p>
The Consultative Group on<p>
Early Childhood Care and Development<p>
</center>
<p>
<p>
 An article prepared for<p>
the section on "Marriage and the Family"<p>
<p>
of the<p>
<p>
Encyclopedia of Third World Women<p>
<p>
Nelly P. Stromquist (Chief Editor)<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
May, 1995<p>
<p>
<p>
