<div align=center><h3>
<div align=center><p><b>CHILDREARING PRACTICES, PATTERNS AND BELIEFS --</b></p></div>

<div align=center><p><b>FROM KNOWLEDGE TO ACTION</b></p></div>

<div align=center><p>A Report of Results and Implications from</p></div>

<div align=center><p>Phase 2 of the Project on:</p></div>

<div align=center><p>This Summary Document was prepared for:</p></div>

<div align=center><p>The Latin American Council of Bishops</p></div>

<div align=center><p>and</p></div>

<div align=center><p>The Regional Office for Latin America and</p></div>

<div align=center><p>the Caribbean of UNICEF </p></div>

<div align=center><p>by</p></div>

<div align=center><p>Robert G. Myers</p></div>

<div align=center><p>The Consultative Group on</p></div>

<div align=center><p>Early Childhood Care and Development</p></div>

<div align=center><p>December 1992</p></div>
</h3></div>

