<html><head>
</head><title>Towards A Comprehensive Strategy
For The Development Of The Young Child
An Inter-Agency Policy Review
</title><body><p>
<b>TOWARDS A COMPREHENSIVE STRATEGY</b><p>
<b>FOR THE DEVELOPMENT OF THE YOUNG CHILD</b><p>
<b>An Inter-Agency Policy Review</b><p>

<p>
March 1993<p>
<p>
UNICEF<p>
Education Cluster, Programme Division<p>
UNICEF House<p>
New York, NY 10017<p>
<p>
<b>TABLE OF CONTENTS</b><br>
<p>
<b>Abstract</b><p>
<p>
<b>I	Introduction</b><br>
	A. Early Childhood Development: Definition of Terms<br>
	B. Programmatic Concerns<br>
<p>
