<p>
56.	Leslie, J. and Buvinic, M. (1989), "Introduction" in J. Leslie and M.
Paolisso (Eds.) <i>Women, Work, and Child Welfare in the Third World</i>,
Boulder: Westview Press.<p>
<p>
57.	Himes, J., Landers, C., and Leslie, J. (1992), "Creating Linkages: Women,
Work, and Child Care," <i>The Coordinators' Notebook 11</i>, Consultative Group
on Early Childhood Care and Development.<p>
58.	UNICEF (1992), <i>Strategies to Promote Girls' Education: Policies and
