</pre>
<b></b><p>
<b></b>There are several forms of support for the unemployed.  Those who loose
their jobs can receive an allowance during the first year of their
unemployment, the sum of which is:<p>
	 70% of the persons previous average monthly salary, or max. 18.000 forints
(if it 	would exceed this sum) during the first 90 days,<p>
	 60% of the persons previous average monthly salary, or max. 15.000 forints
(if it <p>
	would exceed this sum) during the next 270 days.<p>
If one could not find a job in a years time and so his eligibility for the
unemployment allowance is over, he can still receive support from the local
authority, the sum of which is the 80% of the minimum pension at any given
time.  At the end of 1994 it was 6 720 Ft.<p>
<p>
<b>Number of people receiving unemployment support from the local
authority</b><p>
<b>1993</b><p>


<pre>
