</pre>
<b></b><p>
<b></b>86.6% of all caregivers are qualified and 13.4% are unqualified.  6.5%
of the qualified caregivers have also got the top qualification (that is,
finished the 1-year further training course).  The following table shows the
percentage of caregivers in the different age groups according to their
qualifications.<p>
<p>
